Priority: optional
Maintainer: Debian letsencrypt <letsencrypt-devel@lists.alioth.debian.org>
Uploaders: Francois Marier <francois@debian.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), python-all, dh-python, python-nose, python-nosexcover, python-tox, python-docutils, python-sphinx, python-sphinx-rtd-theme, python-repoze.sphinx.autointerface
